OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FTemperatures will quickly rise
OL,6,Facross England and Wales today,
OL,7,Fturning very hot for many with strong
OL,8,Fsunshine and light winds. Cloudier and
OL,9,Ffresher across northern Scotland and
OL,10,Fparts of Northern Ireland with patchy
OL,11,Flight rain at times.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying dry and warm into the
OL,14,Fevening. Clear skies holding on across
OL,15,FEngland and Wales with a warm night to
OL,16,Fcome. Fresher in Northern Ireland and
OL,17,FScotland with patchy cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
