OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAnother sunny and mostly dry
OL,6,Fday across England and Wales as the
OL,7,Fheatwave continues. A small chance of
OL,8,Fa few heavy, thundery showers in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Fresher in northern
OL,10,FScotland.
